{"tid":1125181,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"[震驚五十億人] F.I.R出新歌 主唱不是飛","createTime":"2019-04-25T13:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T16:01:27.000Z","uid":126947,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"af3f7559d5bbdcef0d3d3759d41c2b3d1259822f","tid":1125181,"uid":126947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:52:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LeUMB8GXL7k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLeUMB8GXL7k&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=d6102ade\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LeUMB8GXL7k</a><br />\n新主唱唱腔都幾似飛<br />\n但換左人唔吸引"},{"pid":"fc5e7dc39880db85d8ed563e997b5dc728b6564d","tid":1125181,"uid":78349,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:55:51.000Z","msg":"果兩個垃圾男人又要飛起左主音又要用返人哋個名嚟搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔會再支持佢哋"},{"pid":"dc89afca06b9e2bac6da3e4acca68cda6eb8c930","tid":1125181,"uid":232594,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:37:27.000Z","msg":"叫個兩條友收皮啦<br />\n冇左飛兒既FIR已經唔係FIR"},{"pid":"da0c019204225647c846077e4fc682bda0427a9d","tid":1125181,"uid":36702,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:44:06.000Z","msg":"菠蘿包無菠蘿 <br />\n<br />\n飛兒樂團都無飛兒"},{"pid":"40630877b42c93bb3c17c935fd0309aa01266cfe","tid":1125181,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329ccc42f047aaca1e976827212e57d59bc982ba","tid":1125181,"uid":50920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"後生果個唔係溝左阿飛咩？"},{"pid":"2c